39:51.650 --> 39:52.738
I didn't think you
were going to make it.

39:52.912 --> 39:54.348
You're late, son.

39:54.522 --> 39:55.741
♪ Straight from
here to Gloryland ♪

39:55.915 --> 39:57.482
- I'm sorry.

39:57.656 --> 40:00.572
- Look at the size of this
crowd. Can you believe this?

40:00.746 --> 40:02.443
I mean, it's like they're
handing out free MoonPies.

40:02.617 --> 40:04.750
It's sure something.
I want two of 'em.

40:04.924 --> 40:07.013
- Oh, she's an angel.

40:07.187 --> 40:09.494
♪ You don't need money ♪

40:09.668 --> 40:11.757
♪ You don't need no fame ♪

40:11.931 --> 40:13.976
♪ You just need the Holy Ghost ♪

40:14.150 --> 40:15.325
♪ And the power of Jesus' name ♪

40:15.500 --> 40:18.677
♪ You need a ticket ♪

40:18.851 --> 40:22.289
♪ Straight from
here to Gloryland ♪

40:22.463 --> 40:25.118
♪ If you're a sinner ♪

40:25.292 --> 40:26.554
- [Pastor] As a matter of
