- Uh, isn't, isn't
that the point?

40:44.224 --> 40:46.618
- It's the point, but we don't
want 'em staying that way.

40:48.184 --> 40:49.098
- Don't worry. I'll be careful.

40:49.272 --> 40:51.231
- Okay, you be careful.

40:51.405 --> 40:52.754
Look at the size of this crowd.

40:52.928 --> 40:53.712
There ain't been this
many people in this room

40:53.886 --> 40:55.888
since Easter '62.

40:56.062 --> 40:58.499
I'm telling you, man, this
place is full. It's wonderful.

41:00.675 --> 41:02.198
