41:02.372 --> 41:03.896
- [Samuel] Yes, she is.

41:09.075 --> 41:12.557
♪ If you're a prisoner ♪

41:12.731 --> 41:14.559
♪ Or a preacher man ♪

41:14.733 --> 41:16.474
- My dad always told me that

41:16.648 --> 41:18.998
