♪ Lord, I surrender ♪

52:38.938 --> 52:41.462
♪ Surrender all ♪

52:48.469 --> 52:51.037
[Barry panting]

52:52.604 --> 52:53.518
- Have a seat.

52:58.914 --> 53:01.090
- Daddy, these
seats for children.

53:01.265 --> 53:02.048
- Sit down, son.

53:06.922 --> 53:10.622
Now, I understand that what
happened up there today

53:10.796 --> 53:12.972
is not what we expected.

53:13.146 --> 53:16.541
And Brother Malachi,
I wanna thank you

53:16.715 --> 53:19.239
for your willingness to
relocate from Shreveport.

53:20.719 --> 53:22.373
But I have made a decision.

53:23.678 --> 53:27.639
Samuel will be the new
pastor of this church.

53:27.813 --> 53:29.206
- Dad, come on.

53:29.380 --> 53:30.990
- Now, I know he's
a little young.

53:31.164 --> 53:34.907
- 1 Timothy says an elder
should not be a recent convert.

53:35.081 --> 53:36.343
- And it says in
the next chapter,

53:36.517 --> 53:39.346
"Let no man despise thy youth."

53:39.520 --> 53:41.000
[T.L. scoffs]

53:41.174 --> 53:43.089
Brother Malachi has a church.

53:43.263 --> 53:44.612
Now, I know he's your friend,

53:45.918 --> 53:47.093
but he'll be fine.

53:49.182 --> 53:51.358
- Daddy, the boy's
got the devil in him.

53:52.403 --> 53:53.665
Always has, always will.

53:55.710 --> 53:57.538
- That young man has got
something on his life.

54:00.193 --> 54:02.500
Now, what happened
up there, shoot,

54:02.674 --> 54:04.763
I almost went up there
and got saved myself.

54:06.112 --> 54:07.679
It's a little edgy.

54:10.334 --> 54:13.032
We might need a little edgy

54:13.206 --> 54:16.253
where we are in this
world right now.

54:20.387 --> 54:22.041
How do you feel
about this, Samuel?

54:24.696 --> 54:26.306
- If you believe
in me, I'll do it.

54:30.789 --> 54:32.921
- This is the GCO Handbook.

54:33.095 --> 54:36.011
Memorize it. Learn the rules.

54:36.185 --> 54:38.057
Without rules, there's no order,

54:38.231 --> 54:41.843
and without order,
there is chaos.

54:42.017 --> 54:42.931
Stick to the rules.

54:45.499 --> 54:47.849
- Yes, sir.
[gentle music]

54:48.023 --> 54:50.591
- Well, I don't think
anybody has left yet.

54:50.765 --> 54:54.116
Everybody's still upstairs,
so let's go up and, um,

54:54.291 --> 54:56.989
appoint the new pastor.

