♪ All because ♪

58:29.462 --> 58:31.377
♪ Well ♪

58:36.382 --> 58:38.166
- Barry, I didn't know
you played like that.

58:41.474 --> 58:43.302
That was, that was
beautiful, man.

58:45.086 --> 58:47.828
- I didn't know I had
an audience. [laughs]

58:56.794 --> 58:58.360
you know, thank you
