58:59.840 --> 59:02.060
- You don't have to
thank me. I always have.

59:02.234 --> 59:04.018
That's what brothers do.
They believe in each other.

59:04.192 --> 59:06.281
[both laughing]

59:06.455 --> 59:09.589
I'm just, um...
[gentle music]

59:10.895 --> 59:12.549
I'm glad you're starting
to believe in yourself.

59:14.289 --> 59:15.377
- I'm still working on that.

59:15.552 --> 59:17.249
[both laughing]

59:17.423 --> 59:20.731
[gentle music continues]

